{"tid":2346061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柬埔寨開採出第一滴石油","createTime":"2020-12-30T04:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T04:33:46.000Z","uid":107567,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"45bbee62b965e72b1916ffcf264c80270716e1a9","tid":2346061,"uid":107567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:06:14.000Z","msg":"（法新社金邊29日電） 柬埔寨總理洪森（Hun Sen）今天宣布，暹邏灣的油田已成功開採出石油，為這個東南亞最窮國家之一寫下盼望已久的里程碑。<br />\n<br />\n暹邏灣蘊藏豐富的石油，美國石油巨頭雪佛龍（Chevron）2005年率先在柬埔寨離岸發現石油。<br />\n<br />\n但由於柬埔寨政府和雪佛龍未能達成營收分享協議，因此停止產油。雪佛龍於2014年將油田股權出售給新加坡石油天然氣探勘公司KrisEnergy。目前KrisEnergy 在這個油田區塊持股達95%，柬埔寨政府則持有其他的5%。<br />\n<br />\n洪森讚揚首度開採出石油是「柬埔寨經濟的新成就」。他還在臉書（Facebook）發文說：「2021年即將到來&hellip;我們的國家收到一份大禮，那就是我們的土地開採出首批石油。」<br />\n<br />\n柬埔寨石油開採地點位於西南部施亞努市（Sihanoukville）的外海。<br />\n<br />\n雪佛龍發現該地區富藏石油，柬埔寨因此被譽為東南亞下一個潛在的石油國。柬埔寨政府估計，海域內蘊藏數以億計桶原油。"},{"pid":"bad44ee9e78740a0ec91ac18f5c25e2fb8833768","tid":2346061,"uid":284044,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:08:42.000Z","msg":"得5%....係因為佢本身真係廢到同石油公司無Bargaining power?"},{"pid":"035a08254f7766bc6f1873be47ffb4e0b883fab1","tid":2346061,"uid":64576,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:11:26.000Z","msg":"5%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7535aa5f18bfa600e9c1f6d901a6f1695754e33f","tid":2346061,"uid":1988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:13:32.000Z","msg":"海油嚟<br />\n窮國家無技術無人無物<br />\n邊有資格bargain"},{"pid":"9ce0374a832d98ee06038602e04c3b8ed3b123b2","tid":2346061,"uid":9116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"雖然個油田得5%持有, 但係鄰近既地區仲係柬埔寨政府架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c3519f6567bc848cf48ca7cbaf25e131cc978a","tid":2346061,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"佢哋有技術開採？"},{"pid":"b1f8b4309739575e88f55ab219288fcc893e085d","tid":2346061,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bad44ee9e78740a0ec91ac18f5c25e2fb8833768","tid":2346061,"uid":284044,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:08:42.000Z","msg":"得5%....係因為佢本身真係廢到同石油公司無Bargaining power?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:14:53.000Z","msg":"相信係廢同投資太大加上無辦法開採石油， 今次咁大讓步應該係想練兵吸取經驗。"},{"pid":"a0df172c563c8056850d8d6f216c7b7ed24b5f71","tid":2346061,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:22:59.000Z","msg":"周圍都有油<br />\n係睇要幾多錢開"},{"pid":"86f188d7e6f20f8d9187fb97d82440dd0b1d4ce3","tid":2346061,"uid":4357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce0374a832d98ee06038602e04c3b8ed3b123b2","tid":2346061,"uid":9116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:14:04.000Z","msg":"雖然個油田得5%持有, 但係鄰近既地區仲係柬埔寨政府架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"識玩一定係食夾棍 收過路錢"},{"pid":"828b98177dd66b82fe52b2825c0c5402693ad0fe","tid":2346061,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"油價咁低<br />\n仲要得個5％<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎去賣都賺唔到幾多"},{"pid":"f1cf2d68918f4f76e886bc190fc559d5d9ff35b0","tid":2346061,"uid":275498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"75c3519f6567bc848cf48ca7cbaf25e131cc978a","tid":2346061,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"佢哋有技術開採？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"所以咪賣大部份股權畀外資囉"},{"pid":"a0c26edadab74700f63d9cf058a2f2d2d836407c","tid":2346061,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"